{"tid":1570481,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"和理非唔該走快啲～勇武可唔可以溫柔啲～","createTime":"2019-09-15T05:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T07:20:56.000Z","uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"6f23db07b5ea70fad131b0f3a330d5d97557712f","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:56:58.000Z","msg":"或者大家頂唔順黃之鋒，但大家有冇留意到係德國訪問佢嘅媒體，對佢都唔係好客氣下，不斷追問暴力示威為咗乜？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=929384867410410\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwatch%2F%3Fv%3D929384867410410&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=bd59810b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/watch/?v=929384867410410</a><br />\n<br />\n黃之鋒噏乜，勇武手足或者唔使理。但外國媒體會點樣引導海外群眾，大家真係要諗諗：係街上放個魔法，會唔會放走埋國際文宣組嘅心機？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />有冇其他方法，拖慢防暴推進，等後面有得走？<br />\n<br />\n完全同意勇武手足叫大家走快啲，等佢地都少啲機會被捕。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1570357/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1570357/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n不被捕，不送頭，大家齊上齊落！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n香港人加油！"},{"pid":"608111a4480f714182fa1c5afd6f24b6cf06a178","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:59:34.000Z","msg":"P牌自推<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ba5d58df87271a7ae070e25bd514bca97324e21","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:14.000Z","msg":"P牌自推～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"721fed505ec7756a0907a58add9f6561cc79c1cd","tid":1570481,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"Stand with HK, World Anti-totalitarianism March on 29/9/2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570427</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"094fe7798b44c7fcfc88860a2140ac8a12d2ac69","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:05:10.000Z","msg":"同我入晒嚟睇下區家麟叔叔點講拉攏外國勢力～<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://aukalun.blogspot.com/2019/09/blog-post_7.html?m=1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faukalun.blogspot.com%2F2019%2F09%2Fblog-post_7.html%3Fm%3D1&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=14510c95\" target=\"_blank\">https://aukalun.blogspot.com/2019/09/blog-post_7.html?m=1</a>"},{"pid":"a6a15357e6967a4399c3d5175e9cdf3604a83d6c","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:09:09.000Z","msg":"P牌自推～～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01fd5d781fb08167fcb92adf8a9e06f40eac608c","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:18:04.000Z","msg":"P牌又自推～～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7f6e847b44128b8f69c5ccc2255faaab4b760f","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:23:58.000Z","msg":"P牌繼續推～<br />\n<img s