es/lm2/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n//這可能就是我們整個夏天的寫照，面對世界上最強大的專制政權，各盡所能，打出一種風格和尊嚴，抬起頭大聲的喊We are Hong Kong。足球教給我們的事，不外乎齊上齊落、博盡無悔、有隊友會犯錯但不篤灰、不割席，互相得力，對手強大就每人多走一步，就此而已。//<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/副刊/article/20190915/s00005/1568484308317/這個夏天-實踐的共同體\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A%2Farticle%2F20190915%2Fs00005%2F1568484308317%2F%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9-%E5%AF%A6%E8%B8%90%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E9%AB%94&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=394da513\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E5%89%AF%E5%88%8A%2Farticle%2F20190915%2Fs00005%2F1568484308317%2F%E9%80%99%E5%80%8B%E5%A4%8F%E5%A4%A9-%E5%AF%A6%E8%B8%90%E7%9A%84%E5%85%B1%E5%90%8C%E9%AB%94&h=0f55804d\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/副刊/article/20190915/s00005/1568484308317/這個夏天-實踐的共同體</a>"},{"pid":"6442c97e2a5d587f2d4f748a87c60d3e94317c81","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"721fed505ec7756a0907a58add9f6561cc79c1cd","tid":1570481,"uid":63045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T06:01:31.000Z","msg":"Stand with HK, World Anti-totalitarianism March on 29/9/2019<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570427\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570427</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:46:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fda054c1cd54a78496e3be88be621aee0495929","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T07:59:05.000Z","msg":"P牌再推推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f0ff694550625c770e3cd877e51046d7bca60d","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T08:31:02.000Z","msg":"帖文等你推～<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"654b34d90fc32ff48c69c6419902f5c31bd52b89","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T13:21:57.000Z","msg":"P牌繼續推推推～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47ce42b9adc4802a5ef66da633b1c2a23af71f14","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:24:48.000Z","msg":"P牌推帖兼share文～<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/german.dark.office/posts/3020606241346377\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgerman.dark.office%2Fposts%2F3020606241346377&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=c9fcdd2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/german.dark.office/posts/3020606241346377</a><br />\n<br />\n【唔係人人都食到大辣】尋日去黃之鋒個Forum，未夠鐘已坐爆哂，我同德國佬已經係最後兩個入，仲要坐地下，仲有二三十人入唔到場。經過我嘅觀察，同德國佬嘅解釋，我好明白點解黃之鋒係國際間係咁受歡迎，而相反喺香港會俾人笑左膠戇鳩仔。<br />\n利申，當年2014佢走去保護金紫荊升旗，我都想將佢連埋個金紫荊推落海。<br />\n但大家冷靜聽下我嘅分析。<br />\n首先要明白一樣野，以前大家都覺得梁天琦太過激進，以前講港獨會比人藐，以前阻街會比人屌，以前推鐵馬都會話暴力，依家呢？<br />\n因為唔係人人都可以第一下就食大辣，有啲人由清湯開始食，有啲人有10小辣開始食，當然有啲人一出世就係食大辣。<br />\n今時今日大部份香港人都食到大辣，但大部分德國人唔係。佢哋仲處於汲收緊香港資訊嘅階段。<br />\n你無啦啦逼佢食大辣，佢一下子接受唔到。反而黃之鋒呢啲10小辣，已經令德國人流晒眼淚。<br />\n口味呢家野冇得拗，呢時呢刻嘅德國人係唔受大辣就係唔接受大辣。<br />\n有人話：「外國人示威仲激進啦！」<br />\n佢地習慣左示威激進，所以就更覺得黃之鋒呢啲左膠和理非好可愛。<br />\n正如我隻德國佬見到中菜館道牆有隻大金龍，係咁拉我去影相，我Dllm咪撚搞我。<br />\n德國人唔係反對香港示威者升級，只係佢地更喜歡左膠大愛和理非，「易入口啲」。<br />\n「Dllm黃之鋒唔代表香港人！」<br />\n外國媒體如何揀人去代表香港，係唔到我地決定，連登夠代表到香港呀，外國人明條毛咩，Google translate 完都唔知你講乜。dllm，黃之鋒之前，係成虫代表緊香港呀，我地有得揀咩？！成虫仲係德國佬嘅兒時偶像，我第一句撻過去：「成虫只係一條臭Hi」結果辣得濟，德國佬嬲撚左。<br />\n「黃之鋒今次冇份抗爭，唔好衝出黎奶光環！」<br />\n嗱，查實佢嘅發言講左兩三次，講自己唔係呢次運動嘅Leader，佢係向外國解釋五大訴求、警暴、新屋嶺發生咩事。<br />\n就算佢有光環，都唔係佢控制，大部分德國人講起香港示威就諗起佢，正如大家講起德國，會先諗起「著皮褲、飲啤酒、食香腸」同樣代表唔到德國。<br />\n我一番德國開工，朝早有同事講 &bdquo;Joshua Wong was arrested!&ldquo; 到下午到另一個同事講 &bdquo;oh thank god, Joshua is now released and he&rsquo;s on the way to Berlin!&ldquo; 有冇香港人嘅認同，佢都係有光環。同樣嘅說話、同樣嘅爬入公民廣場，換另一個人，未必可以喺外國媒體得到咁大關注，正如個瑞典女仔Greta ，有邊個估到咁多人聽佢支笛去罷課。<br />\n既然黃之鋒有冇光環，代唔代表香港，大家都控制唔到，倒不如利用佢嘅影響力。要知道，佢個朵仲響過林鄭，尋日佢仲係同德國外長會面，搞到強國要召德國大使抗議。<br />\n佢幾千蚊一張來回機票，換來：<br />\n1. 強國揼春<br />\n2. 場內五毛挑機獻醜<br />\n3. 強國人喺柏林上街抗議<br />\n4. 三大報紙頭版（我地兩次眾籌登報，都係登到內頁咋）<br />\n大家可以無限loop佢嘅膠事，但喺呢個時候，善用利用借用好過割蓆。"},{"pid":"726c32e7b6ae624c73f43812c4e0d4eee6c8e0aa","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T14:58:29.000Z","msg":"P牌日日推～<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce4c8a7cfb5cd77a93d8ba785cb37239c13893ac","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-16T23:34:19.000Z","msg":"P牌不停推～<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09d7e55bd57cf9c5c98bb248d9ddf0964451d7ab","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-17T09:49:02.000Z","msg":"P牌再share文～<br />\nCNN: Hong Kong protests are growing smaller but more violent and ugly<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/09/15/asia/hong-kong-protest-violence-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F09%2F15%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protest-violence-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mP3Ut%2FTlF5atQuTXJDR4vuI%3D&h=ae5e5743\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F09%2F15%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protest-violence-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=4f261c38\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/09/15/asia/hong-kong-protest-violence-intl-hnk/index.html</a>"},{"pid":"1153bbcb70b0937054b072b45f4c93346464526c","tid":1570481,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T07:20:56.000Z","msg":"P牌推極都係零like，算唔算一個記錄？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}